Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙" \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the place that we called the Universe.
