Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.69,0:25:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱德拉射线天文台\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Chandra x-ray Observatory
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.62,0:25:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到银河中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Has caught our galaxy's
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.82,0:25:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超大质量黑洞吞噬宇宙物质的画面 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Supermassive black hole nibbling on cosmic matter
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.66,0:25:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是像其它超大质量黑洞那样活跃 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not bingeing like other supermassive black holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.13,0:25:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们银河系的黑洞比起其它黑洞来说并不活跃 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our black hole is, today, inactive, compared to other black holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.17,0:25:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的星系中央的气体含量很少 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our galaxy has very little gas at the center
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.81,0:25:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以实际上我们星系的黑洞能吃到的物质很少 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And so, there's nothing really for the black hole to feed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.38,0:25:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它吃得不多 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's not eating very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它正处于挨饿节食期 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's going on a bit of starvation diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.62,0:26:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们星系的超大质量黑洞似乎在斋戒 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our galaxy's supermassive black hole appears to be fasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.96,0:26:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部分是因为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is partly due to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.66,0:26:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着银河年龄增大 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That as a galaxy ages
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.56,0:26:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吞食得到的物质越来越少 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Less and less matter is present for it to gorge on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.03,0:26:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在将来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But, in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.80,0:26:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在银河中心 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It might be quite a bit more active
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.94,0:26:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能得到充足的新鲜气体供应的话 它可能会变得更活跃些 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If it ever gets a fresh supply of gas at its center to feed off of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.48,0:26:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复我们的超大质量黑洞食欲的一个办法 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One way to rejuvenate our supermassive black hole's appetite
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.15,0:26:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是与另一个星系相撞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is to collide with another galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.29,0:26:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着难以置信？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sound implausible?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.76,0:26:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两百万光年远处 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Two million light-years away
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.56,0:26:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们系最近的邻居仙女星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our closest neighbor, the Andromeda galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.23,0:26:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正以75英里每秒的速度冲向我们 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is charging toward us at almost 75 miles per second
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.74,0:26:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是说270 000英里每小时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or 270,000 miles per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.49,0:27:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the future
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.49,0:27:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学家们预言这两个星系会相撞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists predict the two galaxies will collide
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.36,0:27:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于冲撞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And upon impact
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.66,0:27:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,较大的星系将会产生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The larger galaxy may engage in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.79,0:27:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中最原始的运动之一 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of the most primitive acts known in the Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.87,0:27:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最野蛮的仪式之一 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's one of the most barbaric rituals in space
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.95,0:27:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,较大星系吞并较小的星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A larger galaxy eats a smaller one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.99,0:27:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅场景不是科幻小说作家的幻想 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The scenario isn't a science fiction writer's fantasy
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.23,0:27:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是宇宙真实的写照 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a cosmic reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.73,0:27:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做"星系吞食" \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's called "galactic cannibalism."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.31,0:28:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当两星系迎头相撞时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ghastly event can occur on the celestial highway
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.48,0:28:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这惊人的一幕就发生了 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When two galaxies have a head-on collision
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.45,0:28:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两星系最终融合在一起 但不是和睦的合并 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Both eventually melt together in a less than harmonious merger.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.49,0:28:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系非常暴力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you're a galaxy, it's very violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会把你撕成碎片 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're torn to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.20,0:28:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约书亚·巴尼斯研习星系融合 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Joshua Barnes studies galaxy mergers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.47,0:28:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表现得像犯罪现场调查者 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Acting like a crime scene investigator
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.88,0:28:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也承认他的研究有点类似观察车祸 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He admits his research is a bit like inspecting a car crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.25,0:28:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象你遇到一个车祸现场 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Imagine that you come across the scene of a car crash
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.82,0:28:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有遇难的车辆没有目击者 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Two wrecked vehicles but no witnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.23,0:28:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人告诉你发生过什么 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nobody to tell you what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.69,0:28:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能调查的只有现场的证据 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All you have is the physical evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.16,0:28:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们研究星系碰撞时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's basically what we have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.93,0:28:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上就是这样研究的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When we study colliding galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.03,0:28:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有星系碰撞的目击者 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So there are no witnesses to a galactic collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.10,0:29:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能调查的只有目前星系撞后的状态 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All that you have is the present state of the wreckage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.17,0:29:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得开展一系列调查\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you have to conduct a sort of forensic investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.04,0:29:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来弄清楚 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To try and figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.69,0:29:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前发生过些什么 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what happened on the basis of what you have today.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.38,0:29:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们迎头相撞 你可以知道 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If they collided head on , You would know
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.02,0:29:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为可以找到压碎的前端 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because the fronts were squashed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.35,0:29:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它们侧边相撞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if they, say, side-swiped each other
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.39,0:29:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在星系相撞中 这种侧边相撞更有可能 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which is actually more likely in galactic collisions
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.63,0:29:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侧边撞留下的破坏痕迹又是完全不同的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That would leave you a completely different pattern of wreckage
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.83,0:29:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以区别出来 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you could interpret that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.10,0:29:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么引起星系融合的呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So what causes galaxy mergers?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.33,0:29:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万有引力 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.87,0:29:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中的任何物质都是在太空中自由穿梭 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everything in the universe is falling freely through space
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.91,0:29:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对两个像星系这样大的两物体 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And when you've got two large objects like galaxies
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.11,0:29:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们相互的万有引力把它们拉近 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Their mutual gravity pulls them together
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.78,0:29:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致相互靠近 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So they fall into each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.72,0:29:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实就是万有引力把物体拉聚在一起 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it's really just the force of gravity pulling things around.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.82,0:29:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天看到的星系碰撞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The galaxies that we're seeing colliding today
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.89,0:29:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们大多都是100到150亿年前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most of them have been bound and destined to collide
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.66,0:30:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就注定要撞在一起的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For upwards of 10--15 billion years
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.56,0:30:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只是在完成它们的第一次碰撞而已 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And they're only now just making it to that first collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.51,0:30:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们银河系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our own galaxy, the Milky Way
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.15,0:30:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在移向毗邻的仙女星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is moving toward our neighbor, Andromeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.82,0:30:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个星系都呈螺线形 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Both galaxies are spiral in shape
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.49,0:30:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是仙女星系约是超大质量黑洞质量两倍 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But andromeda is about twice as massive with a supermassive black hole
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.96,0:30:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太阳质量3千万倍 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The mass of 30 million suns.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.67,0:30:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当两星系相互靠拢时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It'll look a lot like a dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.64,0:30:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就像在舞蹈 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When you see the two galaxies come close together
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.04,0:30:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们如舞蹈般绕着对方 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So they kind of dance around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.08,0:30:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越靠越近 越移越快 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Getting closer and closer, moving faster and faster
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.41,0:30:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它们最终聚在一起前 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Before they finally come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.28,0:30:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在碰撞那一点 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But at the point of impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.65,0:30:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系的舞蹈比人类的脚尖旋转复杂得多 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These galactic dancers will do more than pirouette.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.46,0:31:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个星系都有行星构成的螺线圆盘 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each one has a spiral disc of stars
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.59,0:31:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺线圆盘外围\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then surrounding that,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.13,0:31:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一层暗物质光圈 人眼是不可见的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A halo of dark matter, invisible material
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.97,0:31:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们能够探测到它的引力场 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That we can detect by its gravitational field.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.14,0:31:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两层暗光圈空间范围更大 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These two dark halos, which are much larger
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.34,0:31:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两星系经过时 暗光圈会叠在一起 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will overlap as the galaxies pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.21,0:31:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着两星系螺线式环绕对方 最后越来越近\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eventually, as the two galaxies spiral around each other closer and closer
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.08,0:31:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就再也区分不开它们了 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can no longer distinguish them as separate systems
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.25,0:31:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终 核聚在一起 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And finally, the nuclei merge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.48,0:31:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女星系与银河系冲撞时 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When Andromeda and the Milky Way collide
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.78,0:31:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河系将会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's going
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.25,0:31:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到最大的冲撞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To be the biggest collision that the Milky Way has seen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.25,0:31:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50亿年来一遇 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Something like five billion years time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.39,0:31:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息是我们太阳系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The good news is that we, the solar system
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.33,0:31:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够正面观看到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will have a grandstand view.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.79,0:31:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两星系冲撞的经过 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What will happen is the two galaxies
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.20,0:31:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的螺线圆盘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Their spiral discs
