Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.63,0:32:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞出圆盘时可以鸟瞰到冲撞的整个过程 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And get a sort of bird's eye view of the whole process as we fly out
