Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.73,0:32:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷入正在合并的星系的中央 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Plunging towards the center of the merging galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.77,0:32:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上是难以预测的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's basically no way to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.74,0:32:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系合并过程中 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}During the merger
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.81,0:32:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们太阳系穿过仙女系外圈或边缘 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If our solar system moves through the suburbs or the edges of Andromeda
