Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.42,0:32:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On the other hand
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.75,0:32:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数的行星和太空物质 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Countless stars and space material
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.32,0:32:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会飞向我们太阳系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Could be propelled towards the planets
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.03,0:32:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会扰乱太阳系行星的运行轨道 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Potentially disrupting their orbits around the sun.
