Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.38,0:33:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多星际气体 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Have plenty of interstellar gas
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.02,0:33:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是行星形成的原材料 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The raw material from which stars are born.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.56,0:33:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那意味着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, that would mean
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.49,0:33:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多"零龄主序后星"  "超新星"会远离我们而去 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A lot more evolved stars, supernova going off in our vicinity
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.67,0:33:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一离去将导致震波 冲击波\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that could create shockwaves, blast waves
