Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.90,0:33:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结局非常险恶 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which would have nasty consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.15,0:33:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两系合并后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}After the merger
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.25,0:33:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们太阳系的命运飘忽不定 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The fate of our solar system is uncertain
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.38,0:33:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当银河系和仙女系各自的超大质量黑洞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As the supermassive black holes of Andromeda and the Milky Way
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.36,0:33:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新形成的混乱星系里相互竞争 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Vie for power in the newly jumbled galaxy.
