Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.07,0:34:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个超大质量黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And these two supermassive black holes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.17,0:34:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会逐渐盘旋着驻入新的星系中央 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will gradually spiral into the middle of the new galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.01,0:34:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一对黑洞的状态只保持很短一段时间 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They will be a binary black hole for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.71,0:34:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些黑洞开始吞食气体 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And these black holes will start to swallow gas
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.75,0:34:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲撞搅起太空物质 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As the collision stirs things up
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.18,0:34:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空气体夹着物质卷入黑洞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gas will fall into those black holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.09,0:34:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物质被激发 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're gonna turn on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.82,0:34:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始迸发辐射线 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're gonna start emitting radiation.
