Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.63,0:34:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物质像那样被卷入进去是可能的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Matter falling into them, possibilities like that do exist
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.63,0:34:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观看这一过程唯一安全的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then the only safe place to watch the process
