Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.92,0:34:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将最终吞噬掉银河系的超大质量黑洞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will eventually consume the Milky Way's.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.99,0:35:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个黑洞先是盘旋在中央\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The two black holes will spiral in the center
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.52,0:35:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成一对黑洞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And become a binary black hole
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.96,0:35:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后互相吞并\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And ultimately, will merge with one another
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.96,0:35:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成一个更大的超大质量黑洞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To become yet an even bigger supermassive black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.43,0:35:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 一个小星系撞击一个大星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, a small galaxy colliding with a large galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.84,0:35:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小星系可能被大星系控制 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is likely to be dominated by the larger galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.54,0:35:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终 小星系中的大量物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It'll essentially have most of its material
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.61,0:35:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大星系吸收 附属在大星系之内 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Absorbed by that galaxy and becomes subsumed into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.72,0:35:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学家们认为星系吞并\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists believe galaxy mergers
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.66,0:35:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宇宙中的一种生命方式 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are a way of life in the Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.13,0:35:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括银河在内的现代星系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Modern galaxies, including the Milky Way
