Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.55,0:36:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可能就是先前撞击后的遗迹 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which are, probably, the relic of a previous collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.82,0:36:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多科学家一致认为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most scientists agree that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.12,0:36:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河系与仙女系间这场预期的大冲撞 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the much anticipated merger between the Milky Way and Andromeda
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.02,0:36:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在30亿年内不会发生 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Won't happen for at least three billion years.
