Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.45,0:36:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空中最耀眼 最致命的星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of the brightest and deadliest in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.10,0:36:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"类星体"就是这种怪异的东西 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Quasars are peculiar objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.13,0:37:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类星体由超大质量黑洞提供能量 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each powered by a supermassive black hole
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.84,0:37:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑洞会不停地吞食大量的物质 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That continually swallows large amounts of matter
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.14,0:37:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年吞食10~20颗星体 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}10 to 20 stars every year.
