Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.90,0:37:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类星体拥有宇宙中最高效利用能量的机制 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Quasars are the most energy-efficient mechanisms in the cosmos
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.54,0:37:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它释放的能量比一百个普通星系还要多 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They give off more power than a hundred normal galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.24,0:37:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们的太阳要亮十万亿倍 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And they're 10 trillion times brighter than our Sun.
